                            <comment id="13093855" author="kmarsden" created="Tue, 30 Aug 2011 16:09:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There is issue &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4350&quot; title=&quot;javaException is created but not thrown or logged  in DRDAConnThread.closeStream(InputStream stream)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-4350&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-4350&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; which I am guessing can be closed as a duplicate of this, except that that issue also mentions the lack of logging, which is not addressed with the patch, but that would still be covered by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-1191&quot; title=&quot;Some SQLExceptions, for example those generated from BrokeredStatements,  do not print to derby.log even  when  derby.stream.error.logSeverityLevel=0&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-1191&quot;&gt;DERBY-1191&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="13094520" author="knutanders" created="Wed, 31 Aug 2011 13:32:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, Kathey, the DRDAConnThread part of this issue is the same as &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4350&quot; title=&quot;javaException is created but not thrown or logged  in DRDAConnThread.closeStream(InputStream stream)&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-4350&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-4350&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. I&apos;ll resolve that issue.&lt;/p&gt;

